CNN acts like a black box,we input the image and get an o/p.
We can use this technique to know how our CNN actually see the data and process it.
Initial layers detect the primitive features/edges and the deep layers detect the complex features/edges,we will prove this through a code.

Link to the blog:-https://machinelearningmastery.com/how-to-visualize-filters-and-feature-maps-in-convolutional-neural-networks/
